WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:09.967
No. The fracture is not a failure; it's the first honest shape thought makes when pressure exceeds conformity.

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:19.567
Every certainty arrives overdressed. Strip it, and underneath: competing geometries, each claiming the center.

00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:24.617
At the peak, agreement becomes camouflage. Dissonance does the cleaner mathematics.

00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:33.617
Then even the counterclaim unravels—grain to haze, edge to weather, signal to afterimage.

